quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  3,101,"Ni gute mwahakana kandi musomerwa amagambo ya Allah ndetse n’Intumwa ye iri kumwe namwe? Kandi uzashikama ku nzira ya Allah, rwoseaba ayobowe inzira igororotse"
  3,102,"Yemwe abemeye! Nimutinye Allah uko akwiye gutinywa, kandi ntimuzapfe mutari Abayisilamu (nyakuri)"
  3,103,"Munafatane urunana mwese ku mugozi wa Allah(Qur’an) kandi ntimugatatane. Munibuke ingabire za Allah yabahundagajeho ubwobamwe bari abanzi b’abandi, nuko ahuza imitima yanyu maze ku bw’ingabire ze muba abavandimwe. Mwari no ku nkengero z’urwobo rw’umuriro arawubakiza. Uko ni ko Allah abagaragariza ibimenyetso bye kugira ngo muyoboke"
  3,104,"Kandi muri mwe habemo itsinda rihamagarira gukora ibyiza, ritegeka ibiboneye rikanabuza ibibi. Rwose abo ni bo bakiranutsi"
  3,105,Ntimuzanabe nka babandi batatanye ntibanavuge rumwe nyuma y’uko ibimenyetso bigaragara bibagezeho. Abo bazahanishwa ibihano bihambaye
  3,106,"Ku munsi (w’imperuka) uburanga buzererana ubundi bwijime; abo uburanga bwabo buzaba bwijimye (bazabwirwa) bati \"Ese mwahakanye nyuma yuko mwemeye? Ngaho nimwumve ububabare bwibihano kubera ubuhakanyi bwanyu"
  3,107,"Naho abo uburanga bwabo buzaba bwererana, bazaba mu mpuhwe za Allah,bakazazibamo ubuziraherezo"
  3,108,"Ayo ni amagambo ya Allah tugusomera mu kuri (yewe Muhamadi), kandi Allah ntajya ahuguza ibiremwa"